@prefix : <http://www.example.org/aviation/phak#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

# Proposal only. Do not import automatically into the curated ontology.

